<div class="wp-block-essential-blocks-advanced-heading  root-eb-advance-heading-gb364"><div class="eb-parent-wrapper eb-parent-eb-advance-heading-gb364 "><div class="eb-advance-heading-wrapper eb-advance-heading-gb364 button-1 undefined" data-id="eb-advance-heading-gb364"><h2 class="eb-ah-title"><span class="first-title">Give hope. Change a life.</span></h2></div></div></div>



<div class="wp-block-essential-blocks-text  root-eb-text-h7tyo"><div class="eb-parent-wrapper eb-parent-eb-text-h7tyo "><div class="eb-text-wrapper eb-text-h7tyo" data-id="eb-text-h7tyo"><h6 class="eb-text">Every day, Devine Mercy Foundation provides love, care, education, and a brighter future for vulnerable children in Cameroon and South Africa.<br>But we can’t do it alone — your kindness keeps their dreams alive.<br>💛 Will you make a difference today?<br>Your donation, no matter the amount, helps us provide food, shelter, schooling, and emotional support to children who need it most.<br>👉 Donate now and be the reason a child smiles.<br>Thank you for your compassion.</h6></div></div></div>


